solute -right-6 -top-4 text-xl animate-pulse text-yellow-300\">✨</span></div><span class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl text-neutral-500 font-light tracking-tight\">Rudraraju</span></span></div><div class=\"relative w-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><span class=\"flex w-full items-center justify-center text-center text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-300 font-mono md:min-h-fit md:justify-start md:text-left\"><span class=\"text-teal-500 mr-2\">&gt;</span><span></span><span style=\"color:inherit\" class=\"styles-module_blinkingCursor__yugAC styles-module_blinking__9VXRT\">_</span></span><div class=\"mt-2 h-[1px] w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500/50 to-transparent hidden md:block\"></div></div><p class=\"text-neutral-400 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg text-center md:text-left backdrop-blur-sm md:backdrop-brightness-100 p-4 md:p-0 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800/50 md:border-0 bg-neutral-900/20 md:bg-transparent\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Building the next generation of<!-- --> <b class=\"text-neutral-200\">AI Agents</b>. Currently shipping enterprise automation at<!-- --> <b class=\"text-neutral-200\">Pilvi Systems</b> and building<!-- --> <b class=\"text-neutral-200\">LeSearch AI</b>. Focused on the intersection of<!-- --> <span class=\"text-teal-400\">LLM Reasoning</span>,<!-- --> <span class=\"text-teal-400\">Reliability</span>, and<!-- --> <span class=\"text-teal-400\">User Experience</span>.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4 w-full sm:w-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><a href=\"/resume/Arya_Teja_PM_Resume.pdf\" download=\"Arya_Teja_PM_Resume.pdf\" class=\"group relative px-8 py-3.5 bg-teal-500 text-neutral-950 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-400 transition-all duration-300 text-center overflow-hidden inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(20,184,166,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(20,184,166,0.5)]\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><title>Download Resume</title><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" d=\"M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z\"></path></svg><span class=\"relative z-10\">Download Resume</span></a><a class=\"group relative px-8 py-3.5 border border-teal-500/30 text-teal-400 font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-500/10 transition-all duration-300 text-center backdrop-blur-sm\" href=\"#contact\"><span class=\"relative z-10\">Get in Touch</span></a></div><div class=\"mt-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"group flex items-center gap-1 text-sm tracking-[.2em] opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 active:opacity-100\"><span class=\"hidden md:inline\">Press</span><kbd class=\"bg-neutral-100 p-1 dark:bg-neutral-950 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-500 leading-none hidden tracking-normal opacity-90 md:inline\">Ctrl K</kbd><span class=\"inline md:hidden\">Click</span><span>to explore</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 256 256\" class=\"duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-0 group-hover:opacity-100 md:-translate-x-full md:opacity-0\"><path d=\"M221.66,133.66l-72,72a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L196.69,136H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H196.69L138.34,61.66a8,8,0,0,1,11.32-11.32l72,72A8,8,0,0,1,221.66,133.66Z\"></path></svg></button></div></div><div class=\"hidden md:block relative z-20\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"relative group\"><div class=\"absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-emerald-500 rounded-full blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200\"></div><img alt=\"AI Robot Concept\" width=\"384\" height=\"384\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"relative w-80 lg:w-96 object-cover drop-shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(45,212,191,0.2)] transition-all duration-500\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2FRobot.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2FRobot.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2FRobot.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute -z-50 size-80 bottom-10 right-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(45,212,191,0.15)_0%,transparent_70%)] blur-3xl\"></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center md:hidden\"><div class=\"w-full flex justify-center pb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"absolute -inset-4 bg-teal-500/20 blur-3xl rounded-full\"></div><img alt=\"AI Robot Concept\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"relative w-64 object-cover drop-shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(45,212,191,0.25)]\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2FRobot.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2FRobot.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2FRobot.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:max-w-4xl lg:px-0 pb-28 pt-20 m-auto space-y-28 overflow-hidden\"><section id=\"about\" class=\"w-full py-16\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-3 relative inline-block\">Journey to AI PM<span class=\"absolute bottom-0 inset-x-1/4 h-1 bg-teal-400\" style=\"transform:scaleX(0)\"></span></h2><p class=\"text-xl text-teal-400 mt-4\">My journey from business to AI</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"bg-neutral-800/50 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-8 border-x-4 border-x-teal-400 shadow-lg mb-16 relative z-10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><p class=\"text-lg text-justify text-neutral-300\">From Marketing to AI PM is literally the story of my career. I led high-growth marketing teams, realized the same instincts could steer AI products, and dove headfirst into discovery, prompt design, and roadmap work. The cards below unpack how that pivot produced LeSearch AI, a cadence of scrappy MVPs, and my current search for APM roles where the marketing-to-product bridge sets me apart.</p></div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 size-full z-0 pointer-events-none\"></svg><div class=\"space-y-24 relative\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"relative z-10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-6 text-center\">Marketing Roots to AI PM</h3><div class=\"card-content bg-neutral-800/50 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-6 border-t-4 border-teal-400 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2\"><div class=\"text-3xl text-teal-400 mb-4 text-center\">📈</div><p class=\"text-justify text-neutral-300\">Four years owning growth campaigns taught me how to mine customer signals, brief creative teams, and quantify lift. That frontline marketing context is the foundation of my AI PM work because it keeps me obsessed with the exact users, pain points, and revenue moments we are building for.</p></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-6 text-center\">Building LeSearch AI</h3><div class=\"card-content bg-neutral-800/50 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-6 border-t-4 border-teal-400 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2\"><div class=\"text-3xl text-teal-400 mb-4 text-center\">🤖</div><p class=\"text-justify text-neutral-300\">I co-built LeSearch AI, a GPT-4 research copilot for policy, climate, and venture analysts. I owned prompt architectures, prioritized workflows with the founders, launched features like guided briefs and source pinboards, and let user interviews dictate the backlog that drove retention.</p></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-6 text-center\">Shipping Scrappy MVPs</h3><div class=\"card-content bg-neutral-800/50 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-6 border-t-4 border-teal-400 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2\"><div class=\"text-3xl text-teal-400 mb-4 text-center\">⚡</div><p class=\"text-justify text-neutral-300\">Every week I shipped an MVP—SQL agents for non-technical ops teams, auto-browsing Q&amp;A bots for scouts, summarizers for due diligence—and instrumented each launch so we could cut scope or double down based on activation, not vibes.</p></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-6 text-center\">Searching for APM Roles</h3><div class=\"card-content bg-neutral-800/50 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-6 border-x-4 border-x-teal-400 border-b-4 border-b-teal-400 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2\"><div class=\"text-3xl text-teal-400 mb-4 text-center\">🎯</div><p class=\"text-justify text-neutral-300\">Now I am actively interviewing for Associate PM programs at AI-first teams where I can combine go-to-market intuition with hands-on prototyping. I want to run discovery, scope the AI workflows, rally eng/design, and keep iterating until we show measurable lift.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 text-center relative z-10\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4\"><a class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 border-2 border-teal-400 text-teal-400 font-semibold rounded transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-teal-400 hover:text-neutral-900\" href=\"/resume\"><span style=\"opacity:0\">View My Résumé</span></a><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 border-2 border-teal-400 text-teal-400 font-semibold rounded transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-teal-400 hover:text-neutral-900\" href=\"https://linkedin.com/in/arya-teja-rudraraju\"><span style=\"opacity:0\">Connect on LinkedIn</span></a><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 border-2 border-teal-400 text-teal-400 font-semibold rounded transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-teal-400 hover:text-neutral-900\" href=\"https://github.com/aryateja2106\"><span style=\"opacity:0\">Explore My GitHub</span></a></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"experience\" class=\"w-full mt-28\"><h2 class=\"flex items-center text-3xl font-bold mb-16\"><span class=\"mr-4\">Where I&#x27;ve </span><span class=\"text-teal-400 mr-3\">Worked</span><div class=\"h-px bg-gray-600 grow\"></div></h2><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8\"><div class=\"md:w-64 flex md:flex-col overflow-x-auto md:overflow-visible\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"py-3 px-4 text-left border-l-2 whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-300 bg-slate-800/50 text-teal-400 border-l-teal-400\">Pilvi Systems</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"py-3 px-4 text-left border-l-2 whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-slate-800/30 border-l-gray-700 text-gray-400 hover:text-white\">LeSearch AI</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"py-3 px-4 text-left border-l-2 whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-slate-800/30 border-l-gray-700 text-gray-400 hover:text-white\">mconnect</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"py-3 px-4 text-left border-l-2 whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-slate-800/30 border-l-gray-700 text-gray-400 hover:text-white\">iSpeak AI</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"py-3 px-4 text-left border-l-2 whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-slate-800/30 border-l-gray-700 text-gray-400 hover:text-white\">Duquesne University</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"py-3 px-4 text-left border-l-2 whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-slate-800/30 border-l-gray-700 text-gray-400 hover:text-white\">Sage Wealth Advisory</button></div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold\">AI Product Manager<!-- --> <span class=\"text-teal-400\">@ <!-- -->Pilvi Systems</span></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 mt-1\">Aug 2025 - Present<!-- --> • <!-- -->Dallas, TX (Remote)</p></div><ul class=\"space-y-4 mt-6\"><li class=\"flex\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-hexagon text-teal-400 mr-2 mt-1 size-3 fill-current shrink-0\"><path d=\"M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z\"></path></svg><span>Leading end-to-end B2B AI automation products from 0-&gt;1, shipping 3 MVPs in 8 weeks.</span></li><li class=\"flex\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-hexagon text-teal-400 mr-2 mt-1 size-3 fill-current shrink-0\"><path d=\"M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z\"></path></svg><span>Designed and deployed an Amplitude analytics framework to track complex agentic workflows.</span></li><li class=\"flex\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-hexagon text-teal-400 mr-2 mt-1 size-3 fill-current shrink-0\"><path d=\"M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z\"></path></svg><span>Refined activation loops for technical users, driving a 19% lift in week-1 retention.</span></li><li class=\"flex\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-hexagon text-teal-400 mr-2 mt-1 size-3 fill-current shrink-0\"><path d=\"M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z\"></path></svg><span>Conducting ongoing customer discovery with enterprise stakeholders to align roadmap with business goals.</span></li></ul></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full mt-28 relative overflow-hidden py-16\"><div class=\"absolute top-24 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-md opacity-20 pointer-events-none z-0 blur-sm\"><div class=\"aspect-square rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-700/30 via-teal-500/20 to-transparent rotate-45\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><p class=\"text-center text-gray-400 mb-2 tracking-widest text-sm\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)\">I CONSTANTLY TRY TO IMPROVE</p><h2 class=\"text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">My Tech Stack</h2><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-10\"><button disabled=\"\" class=\"px-5 py-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/20 to-teal-500/20 border border-teal-500/50 shadow-teal-500/20 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2\">Languages<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"size-4\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></span></button><button class=\"px-5 py-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500/20 to-purple-500/20 border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-600 transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2\">Frameworks</span></button><button class=\"px-5 py-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500/20 to-orange-500/20 border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-600 transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2\">Tools &amp; Infrastructure</span></button><button class=\"px-5 py-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/20 to-blue-500/20 border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-600 transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2\">Design &amp; Collaboration</span></button></div><div class=\"h-[40vh] w-1/2 mx-auto my-10 relative bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-slate-900/30 to-transparent rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-teal-500/60 shadow-teal-500/40 shadow-lg\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"relative flex size-full items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><!--/$--></div></div><p class=\"text-center text-gray-400 mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0\">Passionate about exploring emerging technologies and frameworks to build scalable, efficient solutions. Always learning, always improving.</p></div></div></section><section id=\"qualities\" class=\"w-full mt-28\"><h2 class=\"flex items-center text-3xl font-bold mb-6\"><span class=\"mr-4\">What I</span><span class=\"text-teal-400 mr-3\">Bring to the Table</span><div class=\"h-px bg-gray-600 grow\"></div></h2><p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-12 text-lg max-w-2xl\">My core qualities that drive success in every AI solution I deliver</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"h-full bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative group\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500/20 to-teal-500/5 opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"mb-4 text-4xl\"><div style=\"transform:none\">✨</div></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-teal-400\">Positivity</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">Approaching AI challenges with optimism and a solutions-oriented mindset, transforming obstacles into opportunities for innovation.</p><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 size-16 text-slate-800/30 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"absolute rotate-45 size-20 h-2 bg-slate-700/30 -bottom-6 -right-6 group-hover:bg-teal-500/20 transition-colors duration-300\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"h-full bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative group\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/20 to-cyan-500/5 opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"mb-4 text-4xl\"><div style=\"transform:none\">🔥</div></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-teal-400\">Passion</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">Driven by deep enthusiasm for AI technology that fuels continuous learning and delivers excellence in every project I undertake.</p><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 size-16 text-slate-800/30 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"absolute rotate-45 size-20 h-2 bg-slate-700/30 -bottom-6 -right-6 group-hover:bg-teal-500/20 transition-colors duration-300\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"h-full bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative group\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-blue-500/5 opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"mb-4 text-4xl\"><div style=\"transform:none\">🚀</div></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-teal-400\">Ambition</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">Setting bold goals and persistently pursuing advancements that push the boundaries of what&#x27;s possible with AI solutions.</p><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 size-16 text-slate-800/30 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"absolute rotate-45 size-20 h-2 bg-slate-700/30 -bottom-6 -right-6 group-hover:bg-teal-500/20 transition-colors duration-300\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"h-full bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative group\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/20 to-purple-500/5 opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"mb-4 text-4xl\"><div style=\"transform:none\">💡</div></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-teal-400\">Innovation</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">Constantly exploring creative approaches to leverage AI and automation, turning complex business challenges into elegant solutions.</p><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 size-16 text-slate-800/30 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"absolute rotate-45 size-20 h-2 bg-slate-700/30 -bottom-6 -right-6 group-hover:bg-teal-500/20 transition-colors duration-300\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"h-full bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative group\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/20 to-emerald-500/5 opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"mb-4 text-4xl\"><div style=\"transform:none\">⚙️</div></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-teal-400\">Technical Expertise</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">Blending AI knowledge with practical programming skills to build intelligent systems that deliver measurable business impact.</p><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 size-16 text-slate-800/30 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"absolute rotate-45 size-20 h-2 bg-slate-700/30 -bottom-6 -right-6 group-hover:bg-teal-500/20 transition-colors duration-300\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"h-full bg-slate-900/60 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 p-6 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative group\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500/20 to-teal-500/5 opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\"><div class=\"mb-4 text-4xl\"><div style=\"transform:none\">🤝</div></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-teal-400\">Client-Focused</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">Maintaining exceptional satisfaction rates by translating technical concepts into clear value propositions for stakeholders.</p><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 size-16 text-slate-800/30 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"absolute rotate-45 size-20 h-2 bg-slate-700/30 -bottom-6 -right-6 group-hover:bg-teal-500/20 transition-colors duration-300\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"projects\" class=\"py-16 md:py-24 bg-neutral-950 text-neutral-200\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6\"><div class=\"mb-12 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 text-neutral-100\">Projects &amp; Contributions</h2><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">A selection of work I&#x27;m involved in, from active development and experiments to contributions and forks.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"h-full\"><div class=\"bg-neutral-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden flex flex-col min-h-[300px] h-full hover:border-neutral-600/80 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-teal-500/10\"><div class=\"p-5 md:p-6 pb-3 md:pb-4\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-2\"><h3 class=\"text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100 mb-1\">LeCoder MConnect</h3><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors bg-teal-400/10 text-teal-400 border border-teal-400/20 whitespace-nowrap mt-0.5 shrink-0\">Active</span></div></div><div class=\"px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6 grow flex flex-col\"><div class=\"h-[72px] mb-4 overflow-hidden\"> <p class=\"text-sm text-neutral-400 line-clamp-3\">Mobile-first bridge for AI coding agents enabling 100% remote dev workflows. Control Claude Code/Cursor from your phone via Node PTY and Cloudflare Tunnels.</p></div><div class=\"flex justify-start items-center gap-2 mb-4 pt-1 h-[32px]\"> <a href=\"https://github.com/aryateja2106/lecoder-mconnect\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md font-medium transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-500/40 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-neutral-950 border border-neutral-700 bg-transparent hover:bg-neutral-800/60 text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-100 h-8 px-3 text-xs  flex items-center\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> <span class=\"flex items-center\"><div class=\"select-none flex items-center justify-center mr-1.5 size-3.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-label=\"GitHub icon\"><path d=\"M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4\" opacity=\"1\" pathLength=\"1\" stroke-dashoffset=\"0px\" stroke-dasharray=\"1px 1px\"></path><path d=\"M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2\" pathLength=\"1\" stroke-dashoffset=\"0px\" stroke-dasharray=\"1px 1px\"></path></svg></div> <!-- -->Code</span> </a><a href=\"https://lecoder.lesearch.ai\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md font-medium transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-500/40 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-neutral-950 border border-neutral-700 bg-transparent hover:bg-neutral-800/60 text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-100 h-8 px-3 text-xs  flex items-center\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> <span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"ro