3.58579 3.58579C3.96086 3.21071 4.46957 3 5 3H19C19.5304 3 20.0391 3.21071 20.4142 3.58579C20.7893 3.96086 21 4.46957 21 5V19C21 19.5304 20.7893 20.0391 20.4142 20.4142C20.0391 20.7893 19.5304 21 19 21H16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M8 7H16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M8 11H16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M8 15H12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mr-4\">My blogs</h2><div class=\"h-px bg-gray-600 grow\"></div></div><p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-12 text-lg\">Insights on AI implementation, marketing automation, and technology innovation.</p><div class=\"space-y-10\"><a class=\"block group \" href=\"/blog/connecting-terminals-to-web-mconnect\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-teal-900/10 hover:border-teal-500/20 bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-900 to-neutral-950\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"relative h-64 md:h-auto bg-neutral-800 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Connecting Terminals to the Web: The mconnect Story\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-60\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-900/20 to-neutral-900/80 mix-blend-multiply\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1/2 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"p-6 py-8 flex flex-col justify-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"bg-teal-400/20 text-teal-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium\">Featured</span><span class=\"text-teal-400 text-sm font-medium\">Open Source</span></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white group-hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\">Connecting Terminals to the Web: The mconnect Story</h3><p class=\"text-neutral-400 mb-6\">Coding agents like Claude and Cursor live in the terminal, but I wanted to control them from my phone. Here is how I built mconnect to solve the &#x27;coffee shop problem&#x27;.</p><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mt-auto\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-neutral-500\"><span class=\"mr-3\">October 15, 2025</span><span>6 min read</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-teal-400 group-hover:text-teal-300 transition-colors\">Read article<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M3.33334 8H12.6667\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M8 3.33331L12.6667 7.99998L8 12.6666\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></span></div></div></div></div></a><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><a class=\"block group \" href=\"/blog/building-lesearch-from-papers-to-action\"><div class=\"bg-neutral-900/60 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-neutral-800 hover:border-neutral-700 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col\"><div class=\"relative w-full h-48 bg-neutral-800 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Building LeSearch: From Papers to Action\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-70\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/80 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"p-5 grow flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><span class=\"text-teal-400 text-xs font-medium\">Product Engineering</span><div class=\"flex items-center text-xs text-neutral-400\"><span>8 min read</span></div></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\">Building LeSearch: From Papers to Action</h3><p class=\"text-neutral-400 text-sm mb-4 grow\">Research is broken. We read 100 papers to use 1. I built LeSearch AI to turn static PDFs into active knowledge graphs and actionable insights.</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mt-auto\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-500\">September 1, 2025</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300 transition-colors text-sm\">Read more<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.33334 8H12.6667\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M8 3.33331L12.6667 7.99998L8 12.6666\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></span></div></div></div></a><a class=\"block group \" href=\"/blog/why-i-bet-on-open-source-agents\"><div class=\"bg-neutral-900/60 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-neutral-800 hover:border-neutral-700 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col\"><div class=\"relative w-full h-48 bg-neutral-800 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Why I Bet on Open Source AI Agents\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-70\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/80 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"p-5 grow flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><span class=\"text-teal-400 text-xs font-medium\">Philosophy</span><div class=\"flex items-center text-xs text-neutral-400\"><span>5 min read</span></div></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\">Why I Bet on Open Source AI Agents</h3><p class=\"text-neutral-400 text-sm mb-4 grow\">Closed ecosystem agents are a dead end. The real innovation is happening where tools can talk to each other without asking for permission. Here is why I am betting my career on Open Source AI.</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mt-auto\"><span class=\"text-xs text-neutral-500\">November 10, 2025</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300 transition-colors text-sm\">Read more<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.33334 8H12.6667\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M8 3.33331L12.6667 7.99998L8 12.6666\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></span></div></div></div></a></div><div class=\"text-center mt-12\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-6 py-3 text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">View all articles</a></div></div></section></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer id=\"contact\" class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 relative mt-32 pb-6 overflow-hidden bg-neutral-950\"><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-950\"></div><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 stars-small absolute inset-0\"></div><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 stars-medium absolute inset-0\"></div><div cla